Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.12,0:00:09.05,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,3600)\bord1\3c&H1F1F1F&\be6\c&HFFFFFC&}so ra no wo to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.06,0:00:18.66,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}The brilliant glow of this sky, does it carry right into your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.93,0:00:28.63,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,1600)\3c&H141414&}The melody you heard in your dream, it plays like the silence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:33.73,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Even if your hands are still far from that dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.73,0:00:38.70,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Come now and remember that kindly voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.70,0:00:51.31,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(50,200)\3c&H141414&}Someone was there singing for you, singing those chords of happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:01:01.01,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Sound of the sky, echo on high, break through that overwhelming sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.01,0:01:05.85,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Everything that shines in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.85,0:01:11.52,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,400)\3c&H141414&}Is part of the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.52,0:01:20.82,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,200)\3c&H141414&}Even your tears can't leave you here to stay forever
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:33.32,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,4000)\3c&H141414&}In this light pouring down onto you, play tomorrow's song
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.69,0:02:33.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what am I doing wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:35.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.61,0:02:38.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.85,0:02:46.84,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&00&}The Rainy Sky - A Glass Rainbow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:48.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have your wallet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:49.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:50.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And your dog tag?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.47,0:02:50.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.97,0:02:51.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Handkerchief?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:52.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.28,0:02:53.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Tissues?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.06,0:02:53.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.47,0:02:54.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Map?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:54.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.79,0:02:55.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Compass?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:56.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:57.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency rations?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.39,0:02:57.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.77,0:02:58.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Helmet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:02:59.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.67,0:03:00.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Handgun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:02.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand grenades?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:07.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She's kidding, Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.13,0:03:10.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.51,0:03:13.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you thought about it for a second, you would have known.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:16.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't funny, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.22,0:03:21.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two have been getting along really well recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.14,0:03:25.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio is just like an anxious mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:29.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the list for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:31.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:36.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mission is to enter town and purchase the items on that list.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.70,0:03:37.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:38.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:41.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, drive safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.48,0:03:46.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Commencing operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:52.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.01,0:03:55.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're having pot-au-feu for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:57.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come straight home, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:03:57.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:06.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This the first time we've gone into town together, isn't it, Noel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:08.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Though...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:12.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is basically my first time going to town...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:17.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:20.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.92,0:04:26.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It was completely different during the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:30.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's a calm, quiet town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.78,0:04:40.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.16,0:04:44.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The first thing was a Nue. It's a roof ornament regional to Trois.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:47.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's supposed to ward off evil spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.69,0:04:55.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Second was a water fountain. It was modeled after the twelfth Helvetian Archduke, Akira Arcadia II.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:00.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We've arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.09,0:05:04.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Those things?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.71,0:05:06.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Orders were to drive safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.67,0:05:09.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.94,0:05:12.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You really do know everything, Noel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.02,0:05:17.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:21.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you coming in or not? Would you make up your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:23.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're blocking the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:28.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're the lady I met during the festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:30.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Young{\i0} lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:33.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Coercion. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:37.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're as stiff-necked as ever, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:39.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then at least call me Naomi, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.39,0:05:42.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Naomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:56.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So the next shipment is next month?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:06:00.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And does that girl know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.79,0:06:09.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange as ever, you girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:11.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean you're soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:11.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:13.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.02,0:06:14.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:19.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You've were obsessed with it when you first got here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:21.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:29.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but... Can I touch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.78,0:06:42.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A-flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:51.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a fish, isn't it? What kind is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:53.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what was it-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.37,0:06:54.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.09,0:06:56.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.03,0:07:00.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a dolphin. An animal more like humans than fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:03.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A type of sea mammal from when the ocean still had animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:06.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The ocean? They lived in the ocean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:09.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:17.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That old gaffer's good at making stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:21.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He's as much of a romantic as his face isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:23.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the person who made this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:29.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a factory a bit from town. That's where I get all this glassware.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:33.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see them make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:34.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:35.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.16,0:07:38.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading there right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:47.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's why. You had the factory make parts for the Takemikadzuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:51.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. We also had Naomi collect old parts for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:56.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're just amazing, Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:07:59.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're fixing that complicated machine just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.82,0:08:00.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:07.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having a hard time just trying to remember the bugle signals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.60,0:08:11.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not really that difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:16.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Because machines won't cross you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.75,0:08:19.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:22.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are! Your change is ¥2,750,000
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.93,0:08:25.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Do we get that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:29.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Our change is ¥2.75.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:32.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sharp as always, Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:34.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your change.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:36.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:39.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been playing the morning bugle lately, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:44.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Sorry I'm still bad at it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:47.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:50.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put it... I wake up completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.19,0:09:02.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was just thinking that I need to learn so I don't cause problems for the townspeople.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:13.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No fair, Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.67,0:09:17.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come and get me then!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:16.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.90,0:09:21.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow... Oh, sor-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:25.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! You ran into someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:26.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.61,0:09:29.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl at the festival!\NThat clumsy girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:36.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.29,0:09:38.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you're back to health.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:52.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:58.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya, these two had nothing to do with your parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:10:01.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all the same! Soldiers disgust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:07.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get out of town already! Blowing that crappy bugle every single morning - you suck already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.09,0:10:10.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:13.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:14.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That was so rude...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:16.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:18.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That boy was orphaned during the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:21.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That may be why, but when he sees soldiers, he just...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.77,0:10:24.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:26.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:29.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We are soldiers. That is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:32.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:34.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.99,0:10:53.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an3}Sound of the Skies
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:58.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an1}Sound of the Skies
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:12.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. We are soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:16.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When I enlisted, I took the Oath of Paradores.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:18.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I knew what it meant, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.05,0:11:23.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.15,0:11:27.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it right from the start! I can't start doubting myself now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:35.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I need to put time into it and get better!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:38.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be chaos without bugle signals!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.83,0:11:39.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:45.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the glass factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.55,0:11:51.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing, Noel! I've never seen a building that big before!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:12.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So this one's no good either?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.73,0:12:14.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it some aberration?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:17.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The refraction should be just right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:28.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kanata Sorami, a new recruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:30.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:31.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:34.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And, um, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.41,0:12:38.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So about what time does it throw the error?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:40.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The seek time is about the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:42.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The distortion in the peripheral regions was far less,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:44.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but compared to last time the...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:44.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:49.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Once he gets down to something about work, he just won't care about anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.38,0:12:53.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But that gaffer Carl is just amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:59.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He's one of only five artisans in our nation with the title Meister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:05.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,He even won a competition in the capital and presented his work to the Archduke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:10.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria! If you're talking, you're not working!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:11.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:13.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry there, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:16.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even deserve the title, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:20.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't make anything like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.05,0:13:22.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.63,0:13:25.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The lens for the Takemikadzuchi's optical sensor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:27.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the original.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.08,0:13:29.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,To restore the Takemikadzuchi,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.92,0:13:33.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I need two exactly like it. So I requested a duplicate here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.68,0:13:35.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:37.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they're this pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:41.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This lens isn't just silicon oxide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:44.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's infused with sodium oxide and magnesium oxide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.43,0:13:48.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This corrects chromatic and peripheral aberrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.58,0:13:51.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it corrects distortion in the refracted image.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:54.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't know the distribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:14:00.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like a magic item from an ancient past, this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.77,0:14:08.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought glass was just pretty,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:10.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's hard to make, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:16.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In Seize, there are high-quality silica deposits,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:20.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,so it always had small workshops where artisans produced their goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:24.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This used to be one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,0:14:27.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But as the war grew more violent,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:30.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,the need for glass for military uses increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:35.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So this workshop expanded during the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.75,0:14:49.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:52.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I like machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:52.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.75,0:14:57.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But sometimes machines can hurt people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.51,0:15:01.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In the past, the Takemikadzuchi probably
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.11,0:15:02.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,killed hundreds of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:08.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I think machines for killing people
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:10.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,really are scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.42,0:15:14.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:17.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:20.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe what's really scary isn't the machines,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.24,0:15:23.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but the people who used them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:27.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, look at this bugle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:29.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like that when I play it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:32.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but when Rio plays it, it sings beautifully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:35.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think tanks are the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:40.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And a while ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:43.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio let me hear a song from the Takemikadzuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:46.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It sang so beautifully.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:02.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the Takemikadzuchi was a good tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.46,0:16:13.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right! Let's-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:21.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:24.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let her sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:29.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She probably stayed up all night again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:33.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel works so hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:35.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,trying to fix the Takemikadzuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:36.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:39.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl is a real artisan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.35,0:16:44.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If she weren't, I would never have taken this crazy job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:49.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Put this on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:50.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.12,0:16:55.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, you two went by Windmill, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.50,0:16:57.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How's Miss Naomi doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:16:59.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.46,0:17:03.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She called the gaffer a wonderful romantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:07.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Or so it sounds. Isn't that nice, master gaffer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:11.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up! Hurry and get back to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:15.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, he's mad! Back to work, back to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.74,0:17:26.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But is that old technology really that amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.89,0:17:28.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:31.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But the boss always says,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.12,0:17:36.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"No matter how amazing it is, humans made this!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:39.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"There is no reason why we can't make it!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.48,0:17:42.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:42.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:45.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:52.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:57.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There sure is a huge difference between your bugling and Rio's trumpeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:18:01.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always thinking about it. What should I do to bugle like Rio does?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.55,0:18:05.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm practicing as hard as I possibly can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:08.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, look at my lips, they're all swollen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:11.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:16.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much I try to play, the sound won't come out like Rio's.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.27,0:18:20.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I just don't have talent...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.48,0:18:21.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.31,0:18:21.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:26.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Talent is the worst excuse for those who give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:27.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand that here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.53,0:18:30.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything about trumpets.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:36.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's one mistake the young ones always make.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.52,0:18:38.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Young lady,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:40.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,are you trying to force the sound out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.16,0:19:14.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not trying to make it this shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.73,0:19:15.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The glass...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:18.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It wants to be like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.99,0:19:29.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Meister Carl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:20:02.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the sound echo the way it wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.11,0:20:50.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:52.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.13,0:20:57.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the sun came out a bit earlier for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:20:59.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That young lady's quite an artisan too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.24,0:21:01.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:03.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.23,0:21:15.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The tone glass makes changes based on the type and amount of impurities infused into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:18.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Our ears can't hear the difference,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.97,0:21:22.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but someone with perfect pitch should.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.12,0:21:25.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata can test each of the samples you've made
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.81,0:21:28.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,to find the one with the closest sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.75,0:21:30.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If she does, we might just...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:31.91,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.91,0:21:34.26,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,listen to their voices,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.26,0:21:35.37,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,young lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.37,0:21:36.06,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.14,0:21:59.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noel has changed quite a bit since she came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.93,0:22:01.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.09,0:22:02.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.64,0:22:26.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it! You did it Noel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.53,0:22:32.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.64,0:22:42.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've seen Noel smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.40,0:22:57.96,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - put these feelings together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.32,0:23:01.43,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}And sing of how important they are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.61,0:23:19.19,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I was so happy that I cried
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.37,0:23:25.28,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It hurt so bad that I laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.37,0:23:34.06,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But that all just goes to show that I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.29,0:23:38.66,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,800)}Let's just take it easy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.69,0:23:40.29,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}Everybody singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.38,0:23:44.63,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Can you tell me who you're asking to the dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.71,0:23:45.84,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}You're just my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.84,0:23:51.68,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - even though they might waver
Dialogue: 1,0:23:49.27,0:23:51.68,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8\3c&HE5A9EA&}I know, you know, we'll be happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.86,0:23:57.65,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I want us to echo on forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.86,0:23:57.65,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8\3c&HE5A9EA&}Can you count my precious hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.02,0:24:03.65,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}All the usual words can't even describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.91,0:24:09.49,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)}Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.81,0:24:14.44,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)}Can you hear it? Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.72,0:24:26.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(320,180)\c&H020202&\bord0}Next time: A Mountain Hike - The Ends of the Earth
